Dumbbell [S1 - Winner] 2025-11-01 8:06 PM
Challenge Explanation In groups of 4, we're all going to get the link to the same video. Individually, we all receive a different cropped image of the same frame in said video, as illustrated by Zan here https://discord.com/channels/1367508442524287077/1433967256357830716/1434331601516363827 . The goal as a team is to communicate effectively to figure out the timestamp the frame comes from. Rinse and repeat. Strategy Each person tackles their own frame by themselves. They will make a list of timestamps where their cropped image appears in the video. They will relay this list of timestamps to the group. Once everyone has done the challenge in their own time, we figure out the correct timestamps. The timestamp that overlaps across everyone is the correct timestamp. Make sure to be detailed and specific. Take your time and only choose EXACT timestamps. Overlay the image to make sure if you need to. Rinse and repeat for all. (edited)
